RHJ’s Kleinwort Benson to Buy Close Brothers Offshore

-- B y   J o h n   M a r t e n s
-- 
2011-03-10T10:57:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/rhj-s-kleinwort-benson-to-buy-close-brothers-offshore-correct-.html
(Corrects assets under management in second paragraph.)    RHJ International (RHJI)  SA said its
private-banking unit Kleinwort Benson agreed to buy Close
Brothers Offshore Group for 29.1 million pounds in cash.  The Channel Islands operations of Close Brothers will
increase Kleinwort Benson’s assets under management to about 7
billion pounds.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Martens at 
 jmartens1@bloomberg.net  